{"tid":2309482,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【即時新聞】西營盤62歲男子墮樓亡 警方相信案件並無可疑","createTime":"2020-12-02T14:38:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T15:00:04.000Z","uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d842dfafae67c1b15ae14ac089f1ff8f495ea6ca","tid":2309482,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T14:38:27.000Z","msg":"【即時新聞】西營盤62歲男子墮樓亡 警方相信案件沒有可疑<br />\n<br />\n港聞 | 即時<br />\n2/12/2020 20:05<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今天下午4時許，一名中年男子被發現倒卧於西營盤英華臺8號，私人屋苑「鉑峯」外，懷疑從高處墮下，救護員到場證實男子當場身亡。據報，男子現年62歲，警方於現場沒有檢獲遺書，經初步調查後，相信案件沒有可疑。<br />\n<br />\n據警方消息，該男子是中資機構員工的親屬。家屬透露該男子生前患有抑鬱症，曾多次向家人表達輕生念頭。警方錄取口供後相信案件並無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞 | #港聞 | #社會"},{"pid":"07b95cc8f6d1c00e78de21ee5dcaee4ec7ee6bb7","tid":2309482,"uid":281822,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T14:58:52.000Z","msg":"鉑峯唔係私人屋苑喎⋯⋯<br />\n成座比中聯辦買咗嚟做宿舍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de37becd180d40c4425165809bc11783681b6936","tid":2309482,"uid":94454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"07b95cc8f6d1c00e78de21ee5dcaee4ec7ee6bb7","tid":2309482,"uid":281822,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T14:58:52.000Z","msg":"鉑峯唔係私人屋苑喎⋯⋯<br />\n成座比中聯辦買咗嚟做宿舍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T15:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}